# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and on checkout, so the
# Prettier format check (`endOfLine: "lf"`) passes identically on the Linux
# and Windows CI runners. Without this, a Windows checkout with core.autocrlf
# rewrites files to CRLF and `prettier --check` fails on every file.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize line endings.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.webp binary
*.webm binary
